<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19981205.0069 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-05 12:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3005 &Cx1f; var-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCIENCE-MYTHS-REVIEW-     12-05 0860
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SCIENCE-MYTHS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SCIENTIFIC MYTHS THAT ARE TOO GOOD TO DIE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Ill., Mich.)  (The Week in Review) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
Horwitz in Paris for details and prices (Phone: 47 42 17 11; FAX:
47-42-80-44). Latin American points: contact Olivia Vasquez in Los
Angeles (Phone: 310-996-0075; FAX: 310-996-0089) 
(bl) 
 By GINA KOLATA   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
