<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-05 13:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4626 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRADLEY-CAMPAIGN-ART-     12-05 1232
