<DOCNO> NYT19981205.0128 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-05 14:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4652 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NJ-COLUMN-BORDELLO-FU     12-05 0802
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NJ-COLUMN-BORDELLO-FURNITURE-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COMMENTARY: THE LURE OF THE ART OF A SUBURBAN BORDELLO 
</HEADLINE>
  (ART ADV: A photo is being sent to NYT photo clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling
1-888-603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(bl) 
 By JOSEPH BERGER    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
