</HEADLINE>
  
 (info box with HOTHOMES)  (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 
1. Schools. 
2. Affordability. 
3. Freeway access. 
4. Exclusivity. 
5. Nearby shopping and business districts. 
Sources: Realtors and housing analysts. 
